.  If I would have died, so would his druid.  This is why some of the time a paladin chooses to LoH himself than another in his party. (BTW...the druid was able to heal himself back to full once all were dead.)  Sometimes a paladin has to make a quick decision on how to use LoH and sometimes it is the wrong one (including using it on a mob instead<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :x --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/sick.gif ALT=":x"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> ).<br>
<br>
